						<div class="postbody">As an example, Super Mario 3 has 1k CHR ROM switching, meaning it can swap out  64 tiles in a bank. I believe all of its animated tiles are packed into one set of 4 1k banks (4 frames of animation) that are used throughout the whole game.</div>

